  "remarks": "JSC Federal Research and Production Center Titan-Barrikady is a Russian military industry company. The company produces weapons for Russian Ground Forces, Strategic Missile Forces and the Navy, including Msta-B howitzer and Msta-S selfpropelled\nhowitzer. The Msta-B and Msta-S are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
